reviews.review_text:
1991-06-12 great show my favorite performance of summer tour 91 but a bad venue .No dancing or smoking allowed ,they were actually writing tickets to people who danced it was nut's .all the beer vendor sighns were reversable and turned into bail bondsman booths NO SHIT .I think the band felt bad for bringing the heads to such a strict venue and they just ripped. The last two songs were epic by that time evryone just started dancing the cops in to a circle it was nut's. 
alott of people went to jail that night unfortunatly. but the show was amazing . I was in the firt row by the time it was over and jerry just looked right at me "momma momma many worlds iv'e come since I first left home"
